title.rendered: BOSS AIR 12 VOLT AIR COMPRESSOR PX06

content.rendered:
BOSS AIR 12 VOLT AIR COMPRESSOR PX06

Boss Air 12 Volt Air Compressor PX06 available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

12v 100% duty cycle ideal for air suspension use.
Oil less compressor can be mounted vertical or horizontal for easy installation

Specs:

  • PX-06 Compressor
  • Duty Cycle 100%@100psi
  • Max working pressure 200psi
  • 1.8cfm
  • Amp draw Max 23amps
  • Check Valve
  • Braided Hose

Mounting sizes are
85mm centres wide and 225mm centres long

To view the range of Boss Air products available, CLICK HERE!
Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!
